	<a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsbusters.org%2Fblogs%2Fnb%2Fbill-dagostino%2F2020%2F05%2F25%2Fcnn-averaged-4-minutes-day-bidens-gaffe-then-stopped-covering-it&text=" >
